Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.monitoring

Class LogProgressReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.monitoring.LogProgressReporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProgressReporter
    public class LogProgressReporter
extends Object
implements ProgressReporter
    Progress reporter that reports its progress into provided log. Progress measured in percents (from 0 till 100) where just started reporter is at 0 percents and completed is at 100. Progress reporter each 10 percents.
